The text boxes are so difficult to place in the spot where you want it, and will often just bug out and stop working all together, forcing me to finish writing with the pen tool, which is equally as frustrating as the text when it tends to disappear, reappear, and cause you to write things more than you should. The eraser only works half of the time, which is awful because the only other way to undo mistakes made by the pen or highlighter is by using the undo button, which ends up getting rid of half of your work. I've spent HOURS on assignments that should've only taken 10, maybe 15 minutes. I've screamed at my screen more in the past 3 months than I have in my life at this horrible excuse for a piece of software. Hair has been pulled out. Nails have been dug into skin. I'm not exaggerating. PLEASE. DON'T. USE. DOCHUB.
